#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/io_tutorial.rst:2
msgid "I/O Tutorial"
msgstr "I/O教程"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/io_tutorial.rst:4
msgid ""
"Before getting into machine vision topics we're going to talk about I/O "
"pin control on your OpenMV Cam. It's important you know how to toggle I/O"
" pins, transmit and receive serial data, and put your OpenMV Cam to sleep"
" so that you can create a system that's able to \"sense\", \"plan\", and "
"\"act\" in one package."
msgstr ""
"在深入讨论机器视觉主题之前，我们将讨论您的OpenMV "
"Cam上的I/O引脚控制。重要的是您知道如何切换I/O引脚、传输和接收串行数据，并将您的OpenMV "
"Cam置于睡眠状态，以便您可以创建一个能够在一个套件中“感知”、“规划”和“行动”的系统。"

